title: BRIEF-Kennedy-Wilson - Co,Partners Are Under Binding Contracts To Buy Properties ,Development Sites In Western U.S. And Ireland For $224 Mln
text:
Market News  31 AM / Updated 8 minutes ago BRIEF-Kennedy-Wilson - Co,Partners Are Under Binding Contracts To Buy Properties ,Development Sites In Western U.S. And Ireland For $224 Mln Reuters Staff 1 Min Read 
April 19 (Reuters) - Kennedy-Wilson Holdings Inc: 
* KENNEDY-WILSON - AS OF APRIL 18, CO,PARTNERS ARE UNDER BINDING CONTRACTS TO BUY PROPERTIES ,DEVELOPMENT SITES IN WESTERN U.S. AND IRELAND FOR $224 MILLION 
* KENNEDY-WILSON - AS OF APRIL 18, CO, PARTNERS ARE UNDER SEPARATE BINDING CONTRACTS TO SELL PROPERTIES IN WESTERN U.S., U.K. & ITALY FOR $529 MILLION 
* KENNEDY-WILSON SAYS EXPECTS PRE-TAX GAIN ON SALE FROM TRANSACTIONS TO BE ABOUT $102 MILLION - SEC FILING 
* KENNEDY-WILSON - CURRENTLY EXPECTS TO RECEIVE ABOUT $195 MILLION IN NET PROCEEDS FROM REAL ESTATE TRANSACTIONS Source text: ( bit.ly/2JYT2HY ) Further company coverage: (Reuters.Briefs@thomsonreuters.com)
